just like you.

813
00:50:39,411 --> 00:50:42,329
I know you're hurting,
but you're not alone.

814
00:50:42,956 --> 00:50:46,292
There are people
out there that share
what you're feeling.

815
00:50:46,334 --> 00:50:47,793
You never have to do
anything more

816
00:50:47,836 --> 00:50:51,797
